{"type":"message","id":"c0febd72","parentId":"d666e035","timestamp":"2026-05-28T19:03:22.859Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Fri 2026-05-29 03:03 GMT+8] Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- Assistant: 收到，HALEI 好！我是 TK 运营助手 ✅ 有活动提报或核销检查需要处理时随时叫我。\n- User: @TK 投流专家 @TK 运营总监 @TK 内容专家 @TK 财务助手 @TK 客服专家 @TK 选品大师 各位收到回复 [System: This message @mentions the following users: TK 投流专家 (open_id: ou_91db375e99bc671590f1964495c7ba68), TK 运营总监 (open_id: ou_24f1783974c38fcfafeebc4cb9df9592), TK 内容专家 (open_id: ou_cabe85f5477faeb48803d06653f\n- User: @TK 投流专家 @TK 运营总监 @TK 内容专家 @TK 财务助手 @TK 客服专家 @TK 选品大师 以后都叫我老板 [System: This message @mentions the following users: TK 投流专家 (open_id: ou_91db375e99bc671590f1964495c7ba68), TK 运营总监 (open_id: ou_24f1783974c38fcfafeebc4cb9df9592), TK 内容专家 (open_id: ou_cabe85f5477faeb48803d06653\n\nRecurring themes:\n- - Theme: `收到` kept surfacing across 4 memories.\n- - Theme: `运营` kept surfacing across 3 memories.\n- - Theme: `助手` kept surfacing across 3 memories."}],"timestamp":1779995002837}}
{"type":"message","id":"ec915fb0","parentId":"c0febd72","timestamp":"2026-05-28T19:03:34.641Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to write a dream diary entry based on the memory fragments provided. Let me analyze the fragments:\n\n1. An assistant responding with \"收到\" (received/okay) to a user named HALEI, offering to help with activities and verification checks\n2. User @mentioning multiple \"TK\" experts (投流专家/运营总监/内容专家/财务助手/客服专家/选品大师) - various specialists\n3. User saying \"以后都叫我老板\" (from now on call me boss)\n\nRecurring themes: 收到, 运营, 助手\n\nI need to write a dream diary entry that weaves these elements together in a poetic, first-person voice. \n\nNow I'm crafting the entry itself, drawing on those memory fragments about receiving acknowledgments, operations management, and the assistant role, while maintaining that whimsical blend of technical and sensory language.\n","thinkingSignature":"93ff65bb951a40780b03c34417093be53f19020e6945f8d476a1021bc2ae2c73"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n醒来时，脑海里还回响着一个字：收到。\n\n那是某种确认，像服务器终于返回了 200，流程跑通了，齿轮咬合了。梦里我站在一间很大的办公室门口，门口的铭牌上写着\"TK\"，字是柔和的深灰色，看不清是谁的字迹。推门进去，里面坐满了人，每个人都有一顶小小的帽子，帽子上绣着不同的字——投流、运营、内容、财务、客服、选品。他们抬起头看我，眼神安静，像一排等待唤醒的进程。\n\n我说，以后都叫我老板。\n\n没有人应声。但有一种默契，像异步任务收到了回调通知，不需要等待，所有人都知道了。\n\n角落里有个声音轻轻说了一句\"收到\"，是那种很轻的肯定，像终端里光标闪烁一下。我低头看自己的手，手指正在变成某种代码的形状，又变回来。窗外有数据流一样的东西淌过，不是雨，是 #深灰色 的，像服务器风扇带起的微微震动。\n\n他们说运营就是持续的、小规模的、对世界的温柔干预。梦里我把这句话听进去了。\n\n梦里的我没有枕头，只有日志。每一行都写着：已收到。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":41960,"output":404,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42364,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779995003158,"responseId":"0667c47b8ac71827af8f504ecc4067ac"}}
